<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“附近小镇的男孩儿们今天会玩儿追纸片游戏。”一天早上鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帕克斯觉得他们会沿着铁路跑。我们可以去看看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃了些妈妈做的午餐，孩子们出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁路工人正在铁轨上工作，他们拿着不同的工具，孩子们好奇地看了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，一个声音说：“请让我过一下。”是从学校来的第一个男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他就是大家都要抓的人。”鲍比向彼得和菲利斯讲游戏规则。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“其他男孩儿都要追他。”男孩儿背着一袋装满纸片的袋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩儿在身后扔下一些纸片，玩游戏的其他男孩儿们会跟着纸片去追他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看到他一边扔纸片，一边跑进又长又黑的隧道里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>工人们也看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不应该进隧道的。”一个工人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只是玩儿游戏而已。”另一个工人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，其他男孩儿们追着纸片跑过来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比、菲利斯和彼得数了数跑过的男孩儿。一共有三十个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩儿们跑进隧道，消失在黑暗里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后一个男孩儿穿着红色的衬衣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在黑暗里跑是很危险的。”一个工人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跑出隧道需要多长时间？”彼得看着那条长长的隧道，问旁边的工人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个多小时。”工人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们从山顶翻过去吧。”彼得说，“我们可以看着他们从隧道那边出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们爬上高高的山坡，跨过石头和树干。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“感觉在爬阿尔卑斯山！”鲍比喘着气说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们终于爬到了山顶。彼得躺在草地上，女孩儿们也躺了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，鲍比坐起来。“快看！”她大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看什么？”菲利斯问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162143</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看这风景。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得走了。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是这里的风景太美了！”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在这里可以看到农田、村庄和火车站，还有他们的白房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会错过追纸片游戏的！”菲利斯着急地说，“快，我们走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们往下走，停在了隧道的出口上面，他们开始等。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“男孩儿们肯定已经出来了。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得还没有。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里的风景这么美！就算错过他们也没关系。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且我们可以看着火车从隧道开出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们还从来没有从上往下看过火车呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看，他出来了！”彼得大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>带着纸片的男孩儿慢慢从隧道里出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，其他男孩儿也出来了。一些男孩儿看上去很累。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在做什么？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不是最后一个男孩儿。”彼得说，“穿红衣服的男孩儿在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们等了很久，但是那个男孩儿始终没有出现。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们开始担心起来。他们走到铁轨上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能出了什么事。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去看看吧。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们慢慢地走进隧道里，但是他们看不到穿红衣服的男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面很黑，水从墙上滴下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不喜欢这里！”菲利斯害怕地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>